Document production, distribution & Issue Status.

Dawn Alleman, the BT Client Relationship Manager for ntl Group, is responsible for the production and distribution of the Customer Contact document. 
The document will be distributed to the people in the contact directory shown in the next section.
This document replaces all previous contact documents. 

Changes to this document will only be made with the agreement of both parties’ representatives.

