Document Changes & Review 

Formal document review will take place every six months.

Smaller changes will be agreed at the monthly Service Review meetings or on an “as and when required” basis. It is the BT Client Development Managers responsibility to effect any changes and distribute the latest version, ensuring the issue status reflects the amendments.



